<plot>In the thirties, during the Fascist Dictatorship, an insurance broker, Omero Battifiori (Nino Manfredi), reaches a small country town from Rome seeking for new customers. The main authorities, expecting an incognito inspection from the Fascist Party of the capital, suspect him to be the inspector and a very important member of the Party. The misunderstanding leads to a number of equivocals until Omero reveals his identity.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?216960</url></doc>
